title: #88: Hidden In Plain Sight With 2Mex
description: Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  Sam and Ryan welcome underground rapping superstar 2mex back to the studio to discuss the world of the Illuminati.  Thank you for your support.
